{"DEPUCELATE":[{"def":"To deflour; to deprive of virginity.","pos":""}],"DEPUDICATE":[{"def":"To deflour; to dishonor.","pos":""}],"DEPULSION":[{"def":"A driving or thrusting away.","pos":""}],"DEPULSORY":[{"def":"Driving or thrusting away; averting.","pos":""}],"DEPURATE":[{"def":"Depurated; cleansed; freed from impurities.","pos":""}],"DEPURATION":[{"def":"The act or process of depurating or freeing from foreign or impure matter, as a liquid or wound.","pos":""}],"DEPURATIVE":[{"def":"Purifying the blood or the humors; depuratory.","pos":""},{"def":"A depurative remedy or agent; or a disease which is believed to be depurative.","pos":""}],"DEPURATOR":[{"def":"One who, or that which, cleanses.","pos":""}],"DEPURATORY":[{"def":"Depurating; tending to depurate or cleanse; depurative.","pos":""}],"DEPURE":[{"def":"To depurate; to purify.","pos":""}],"DEPURGATORY":[{"def":"Serving to purge; tending to cleanse or purify.","pos":""}],"DEPUTABLE":[{"def":"Fit to be deputed; suitable to act as a deputy.","pos":""}],"DEPUTATION":[{"def":"The act of deputing, or of appointing or commissioning a deputy or representative; office of a deputy or delegate; vicegerency.","pos":""},{"def":"The person or persons deputed or commissioned by another person, party, or public body to act in his or its behalf; delegation; as, the general sent a deputation to the enemy to propose a truce.","pos":""}],"DEPUTATOR":[{"def":"One who deputes, or makes a deputation.","pos":""}],"DEPUTE":[{"def":"To appoint as deputy or agent; to commission to act in one's place; to delegate.","pos":""},{"def":"To appoint; to assign; to choose.","pos":""}],"DEPUTIZE":[{"def":"To appoint as one's deputy; to empower to act in one's stead; to depute.","pos":""}],"DEPUTY":[{"def":"One appointed as the substitue of another, and empowered to act for him, in his name or his behalf; a substitute in office; a lieutenant; a representative; a delegate; a vicegerent; as, the deputy of a prince, of a sheriff, of a township, etc.","pos":""},{"def":"A member of the Chamber of Deputies.","pos":""}]}